data.title: technic launcher quits after login
data.meta_description: Launcher Version: 1.0.2.0 (TEKKIT) Operating System: Mac OS X v.10.7.5 Java Version: 7 Antivirus Program: Description of Problem: The technic launcher quits right after I login to it. I already tried downgrading java but it did not work. PLEASE HELP TEKKIT SO GREAT LOTS OF PEOPLE ON SERVER COUNT ...

I use a Mac and have played tekkit on it before. I used to just play on normal tekkit till a friend of mine set up a server for me. About a month ago I tried to open it one day and It wouldn't work. Since then he has had a look at it and can't find any problems. We tried loads of things, including reinstalling the technic launcher, keeping a copy of my technic and tekkit files on a memory stick, removing the memory stick from the mac and then deleting all tecknic and tekkit files and downloading & reinstalling the technic launcher and files. Im checking my Java files right now but it says I have the latest version of Java.

Whenever I open the technic launcher and try to log into Tekkit, not even my server on it, my minecraft guy is on the left and my user name and password are already typed in. I press log in and the screen goes white then the program closes. Im not sure what to do. Help please.
